sequenceDiagram
    participant D as Disk (MEMORY.md)
    participant S as MemoryStore
    participant P as System Prompt (frozen)
    participant A as Agent
    participant T as Tool Response (live)

    Note over D,T: Session Start
    D->>S: load_from_disk()
    S->>P: capture frozen snapshot
    P->>A: inject into system prompt\n(never changes mid-session)

    Note over D,T: Turn 1 — Agent learns new fact
    A->>S: memory(add, "User is in docker group")
    S->>S: injection scan (check for threats)
    S->>D: atomic write (temp + os.replace)
    D->>T: tool response shows LIVE state
    Note over P: System prompt UNCHANGED\nPrefix cache preserved

    Note over D,T: Turn 2 — Agent reads memory tool
    A->>T: memory(action="read")
    T->>A: shows NEW entry in live state
    Note over P: Still frozen from session start

    Note over D,T: Next Session Start
    D->>S: load_from_disk() — now includes new entry
    S->>P: new frozen snapshot (with new entry)
    P->>A: NEW entry now in system prompt
